
Compiling
=========

You will need maven. Then, in the top folder of the checkout:

mvn clean install

or 

mvn clean install -Pquick  		# no tests


Eclipse
=======

In the top folder of the checkout:

mvn eclipse:eclipse

and Eclipse:File->Import->Existing projects into workspace. You're set. With
M2Eclipse, just use "import existing maven project".


Sonatype/ release push
======================

mvn clean deploy -Prelease  		# snapshot deploy, create single-JAR version,
                                    # javadocs, etc.

